metadata.name: Interwoven
metadata.description:
The moving chains of interlocking structures.

Structurally endless, this composition is dynamic. Modifying the algorithm will give it an infinity of new contexts.

It’s possible that the most interesting variations in these images are the gravitational anomalies.

The geometric expression of the infinite variation defies the definition of a singular object; it’s a chain of interlocking structures; interwoven.

Original fractal formula and sound design.

Revisiting a three-dimensional fractal formula from the year 2019.

The Fractalogist.
